FBIS3-53979 "drnes014_o_94002" FBIS-NES-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 SYRIA Al-Shar', U.S. Congressmen Discuss Geneva Summit JN2001140694 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1215 GMT 20 Jan 94 JN2001140694 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar' this morning received a mixed Democratic and Republican Congressional team led by Mr. Tom Lantos. Dr. Majdi al-Jazzar, chief of the U.S. Desk, and the U.S. charges d'affaires in Damascus were present at the meeting. They reviewed the Geneva summit between Presidents Hafiz al-Asad and Bill Clinton and its impact on the chances for a just and comprehensive peace in the Middle East. They also explored ways to bring about an improvement in relations between Syria and the United States.
